{"tid":1379782,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"五大訴求first priority 一定係雙普選","createTime":"2019-07-29T00:29:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T02:02:30.000Z","uid":262264,"like":76,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"aa07c023f688d23f5250f6c0565f9dc88b90a55f","tid":1379782,"uid":262264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T00:29:17.000Z","msg":"請各位睇睇以下文章<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/972393926144079/posts/2560564017327054?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F972393926144079%2Fposts%2F2560564017327054%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=2WRE5dcwgWUU%2Ft06b4Zyyw9axkDoCoA19ZsVt7gViHY%3D&h=68708a07\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/972393926144079/posts/2560564017327054?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n支持成立獨立調查委員會的人，要問自己幾個問題：<br />\n<br />\n這個委員會有沒有權力宣判罪在王志民、盧偉聰和林鄭？<br />\n<br />\n有沒有權力調查中聯辦干政？<br />\n<br />\n有沒有權力決定解散內閣（即行政會議）？<br />\n<br />\n有沒有權力刑事檢控盧偉聰和林鄭、轉介司法審判？<br />\n<br />\n有沒有權力將虐待市民的警員革職？<br />\n<br />\n有沒有權力監督警隊內部改革，甚至遣散警隊？<br />\n<br />\n有沒有權力&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n口講話「獨立調查」，但誰委任誰去查呢？大家心知肚明，最後只是監警會的翻版。<br />\n<br />\n他們將會在一年半載後對市民說：我們強烈譴責xxxx，建議政府xxxx。建議咋，最終個決定權，仍然在中聯辦和特首手上。<br />\n<br />\n「我哋會深切反省同檢討，積極回應市民訴求&hellip;&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n倫敦的「獨立人民法庭」去年裁定中共活摘囚犯器官是犯下「反人類罪行」，然後呢？中共受到甚麼懲罰？政體罪成，又有誰可懲罰政體？<br />\n<br />\n劉兆佳都講到明：成立獨立委員會可以幫政府買些時間。<br />\n<br />\n買時間幹甚麼？<br />\n<br />\n瓦解抗爭。<br />\n<br />\n但我都支持成立獨立調查委員會。<br />\n<br />\n條件是，70個調查委員都必須由全港直選產生，成為當然議員，取締功能組別。<br />\n<br />\n刑不上大夫，也刑不上黨官，甚至刑不上幾萬個警察，試問查來幹甚麼？<br />\n<br />\n你會要求李鵬成立獨立調查委員會調查天安門事件嗎？<br />\n<br />\n永遠只有新政府上台，才有權查前朝。習近平有權查李鵬，文在寅有權查朴槿惠。<br />\n<br />\n邊個有權查林鄭同中聯辦？答案得兩個：一係你叫中紀委干預香港內政，一係成立民選政府港人審港。<br />\n<br />\n只可惜，很快就沒有機會查盧偉聰了&mdash;&mdash;因為他在11月將會脫離港共政權，投奔中共體系。<br />\n<br />\n作者"},{"pid":"208d2e17b48c021973cb61c7728fc94144381b21","tid":1379782,"uid":262264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T00:29:43.000Z","msg":"光復香港<br />\n時代革命"},{"pid":"2466df1a82229f8ec4ddf6c5e9648b50cca9212c","tid":1379782,"uid":262264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T00:30:06.000Z","msg":"光復香港<br />\n時代革命"},{"pid":"d8a48bb8d3dae5d6b063d27f674c7bc8d70a4896","tid":1379782,"uid":262264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T00:30:17.000Z","msg":"光復香港<br />\n時代革命"},{"pid":"3bab9fb5a5d114ceb4e09d47c4d74cfba6f4dc48","tid":1379782,"uid":262264,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T00:31:03.000Z","msg":"光復香港<br />\n時代革命"},{"pid":"04ecb73aabd317d8539728d3b616cf80b2d5e1d0","tid":1379782,"uid":262264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T00:32:42.000Z","msg":"光復香港<br />\n時代革命"},{"pid":"342f18a796024ac4cc085acbd85bcdbbb846c623","tid":1379782,"uid":6528,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T00:33:35.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n想比更多人知道其實而家呢一刻基本上得番香港獨立呢條路，<br />\n我知好多人未準備好，我知而家急唔黎。<br />\n但係想大家思考下，種下一個思想，唔好屌我住。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家就算有真普選其實都係under中共！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁唔通去到2047再抗爭過咩，西方國家都出唔到手幫你地。<br />\n因為白紙黑字寫明50年，西方國家唔好話出手，連發聲既正當性都冇啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可能好多前人都係到諗點解英國當時唔寫999年！<br />\n可能好多我地呢代既諗點解上一代冇去抗爭！<br />\n可能好多下一代係2047係到諗點解我地唔直接爭取獨立！！！<br />\n<br />\n2047到時只會都係變返中國，仲要一下子就變，一定好多人接受唔到。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所有問題去到最後只會追究到主權問題，希望大家思考下。<br />\n今次搞到咁大真係最後一次反擊同最大力量。<br />\n<br />\nBTW，五大訴求，缺一不可！"},{"pid":"d76e4c7041bc6dc52b7c9848ab15b59d8804bb10","tid":1379782,"uid":267311,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T00:34:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">雙普選</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bdff5598d7d5514f243d8d9943f772ef45681dc","tid":1379782,"uid":267311,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T00:35:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">雙普選</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fae7c0352148cd2143ddc64a1b5886edf4a75d2e","tid":1379782,"uid":267311,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T00:35:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">雙普選</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"278f79b869e70698ed0e559d4da728129e8c1976","tid":1379782,"uid":267311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T00:35:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">雙普選</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img sr